OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778069461
OL,3,CNo points deduction for Sheffield
OL,4,CWednesday as Storch takeover complete
OL,6,FSheffield Wednesday's long takeover
OL,7,Fsaga is finally over after US
OL,8,Fconsortium Arise Capital Partners
OL,9,Fcompleted its purchase of the club.
OL,11,FThe club was set to start the 2026-27
OL,12,Fseason with a 15-point deduction but
OL,13,Fthat has been waived by the EFL.
OL,15,FThe already-relegated Championship
OL,16,Fclub announced the news on the pitch
OL,17,Fahead of the last fixture of the
OL,18,Fcampaign, at home to West Brom.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
