FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778069461
OL,3,CNo points deduction for Sheffield
OL,4,CWednesday as Storch takeover complete
OL,6,FDavid Storch, who led the consortium,
OL,7,Fwas introduced to a rapturous welcome
OL,8,Fto officially bring a painful chapter
OL,9,Fto a conclusion after financial
OL,10,Fproblems had impacted the Owls in
OL,11,Frecent years under old owner Dejphon
OL,12,FChansiri .
OL,14,FThe woes looked set to roll into next
OL,15,Fseason, but the EFL said a point
OL,16,Fdeduction would no longer be
OL,17,F"appropriate."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
