CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778069461
OL,3,CNo points deduction for Sheffield
OL,4,CWednesday as Storch takeover complete
OL,6,FA statement from the EFL said the sale
OL,7,Fto Arise Capital Partners LLC, a
OL,8,Fconsortium led by David Storch,
OL,9,Falongside Michael Storch and Tom
OL,10,FCostin, has been completed.
OL,12,F"This has been an incredibly
OL,13,Fchallenging and complex situation for
OL,14,Fall parties, and as such the EFL Board
OL,15,Fhas exercised its discretion, as
OL,16,Fprovided by the Insolvency Policy, and
OL,17,Fconcluded that it would not be
OL,18,Fappropriate to impose a 15-point
OL,19,Fdeduction on the Club following its
OL,20,Fexit from Administration."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
