OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778069461
OL,3,CNo points deduction for Sheffield
OL,4,CWednesday as Storch takeover complete
OL,6,FWednesday have been up for sale since
OL,7,Ftheir much-maligned former owner, Thai
OL,8,Fbusinessman Dejphon Chansiri, finally
OL,9,Fleft the club in October following
OL,10,Fmonths of financial woes.
OL,12,FThe Owls were deducted points
OL,13,Ffollowing his departure and remained
OL,14,Funder various embargoes amid tax debts
OL,15,Fand after failing to pay players and
OL,16,Fstaff on time.
OL,18,FThe club remains under a budget
OL,19,Frestriction for the next two seasons
OL,20,Fbut it will be allowed to sign new
OL,21,Fplayers, the EFL confirmed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
