CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778069461
OL,3,CNo points deduction for Sheffield
OL,4,CWednesday as Storch takeover complete
OL,6,FDavid Storch said the sale "secures
OL,7,Fthe long-term future of the club and
OL,8,Fmarks the beginning of a new era for
OL,9,FSheffield Wednesday - one built on
OL,10,Fstability, responsibility, and renewed
OL,11,Fbelief."
OL,13,FHe also thanked and praised the fans
OL,14,Ffor their support.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
