FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778069461
OL,3,CNo points deduction for Sheffield
OL,4,CWednesday as Storch takeover complete
OL,6,F"We know trust must be earned. We are
OL,7,Fhumbled by the opportunity, we take
OL,8,Fthis seriously as stewards of this
OL,9,Fincredible club - we will approach
OL,10,Fthis with humility, transparency, and
OL,11,Fa long-term commitment to doing things
OL,12,Fthe right way.
OL,14,F"To our supporters: thank you for your
OL,15,Fincredible passion and loyalty...
OL,16,FToday, this Club is reborn - and we
OL,17,Flook forward with determination to the
OL,18,Fwork that lies ahead."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
